r** (`llvm/include/llvm/Passes/PassBuilder.h`): High-level pipeline construction API\n- **PassBuilderPipelines.cpp** (`llvm/lib/Passes/PassBuilderPipelines.cpp`): Implementation of optimization pipelines\n- **PassSupport.h** (`llvm/include/llvm/PassSupport.h`): Macros for pass registration\n- **PassRegistry.def** (`llvm/lib/Passes/PassRegistry.def`): Static declaration of all built-in passes"
